1- Create a new Maven Project
1- Delete Main folder because developers use it
2- Add dependencies for Selenium
3- Add dependencies for WebDriver
4- Test run to see if it is working

driver.get(url) : open url
driver.navigate().to(url) : load a new page in the current browser
driver.navigate().back() : move in the browser history to the previous one
driver.navigate.forward() : move forward in the browser history
driver.navigate.refresh(): load new web page in the current window
driver.close() - will close only current window
driver.quit(). will close all windows opened by browser


